<h2>The FreeCEN Development Roadmap</h2>

<div class="lead">
<p>There is a roadmap which sets out the plan for the development of the FreeCEN2 software. The plan is split into a number of ‘versions’, each of which is specified to benefit a particular actor (user or volunteer) and outlines the high-level features or areas we expect to deliver or address for them. 
</p>
